  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released on: 9/02/16 10:58 CT</p><p>This is a minor release with\u00a0a few bug fixes.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.4-TicketCustomForms\">Ticket Custom Forms</h3><p>The custom forms &quot;required when&quot; setting was\u00a0not functioning properly since\u00a0RepairQ 1.8.3. This update restores the enforcement of custom form requirements.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.4-InventoryImport\">Inventory Import</h3><p>We changed\u00a0the inventory import template column header &quot;Catalog Item&quot; to &quot;Name&quot; so that it matches the expected column headers expected for importing.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.4-ReportExports\">Report\u00a0Exports</h3><p>Several report exports were cutting off number values that contained commas. Any numbers\u00a0trailing commas were dropped from the value. This issue has been resolved.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.4-TicketImport\">Ticket Import</h3><p>Adding services to a ticket with an import was not working properly due to the header column names not mapping to the import file\u00a0</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.4-Listen360Integration\">Listen360 Integration</h3><p>Updated ticket export format from .xlsx to .csv.</p>",
      "representation": "export_view",
